    The library class deals with managing and populating the arraylist of Materials for UserInterface and the GUI's to use.
    Material
    An abstract class with a dynamic type of Book or Periodical.

    Periodical is a subclass to Material, it's defining traits are having genre, issue, and volume, and passing the callNumber and title to the super class.
